name: Hypercube-33 Colorful Play
description: One of the earlier Trapcode TAO experiment after the beta, I was testing color additive and the LINE hard code feature that makes a line from the path between 2 light objects, I didn't even know what I was doing, but it gave some nice outputs. [04-05-16] I re-rendered it so it pauses longer on the stops 1080x1080 | 1:1 | 360frames | 30 fps |
